  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "SR-2 \"Udav\" 9x21毫米手枪",
      "en": "SR-2 Udav 9x21mm pistol"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Udav",
      "en": "Udav"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "SR-2\"Udav\"（俄文Удав意为\"蟒蛇\"，GRAU代号6P72）是一款俄罗斯研制的9×21毫米枪管短后座原理半自动手枪。该枪由中央精密机械工程研究所于2019年推出，旨在取代俄军现役的马卡洛夫PM手枪，并在发布次月通过军方测试。相比马卡洛夫手枪，该设计进行了多项改进来提供较前身更高的改装灵活性：提升握持舒适度的带有防滑纹路聚合物套筒、双侧对称操控机构、集成式配件导轨，以及可更换式瞄具系统。",
      "en": "The SR-2 Udav (Удав - “Boa”, GRAU Index - 6P72) is a Russian 9×21mm short-recoil-operated semi-automatic pistol. It was released by Central Scientific - Research Institute of Precision Machine Engineering (TsNIITochMash) in 2019 as a replacement for the Makarov PM for the Russian military and passed military trials the month following its release date. The design has many improvements over the Makarov including a polymer frame with better texturing for more comfort, ambidextrous controls, a dedicated accessory rail built into the frame, and removable sights to offer more flexibility than its predecessor."
    },
